\begin{document}$$ {\text{MeHg}} - {\text{NH}}^{ + }_{3}  $$\end{document} ion. This is confirmed by the occurrence of the same fragment in MS2 at m/z 231 (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\usepackage{wasysym} 
\usepackage{amsfonts} 
\usepackage{amssymb} 
\usepackage{amsbsy}
\usepackage{mathrsfs}
